        <span id="BookReviewTitle" class="BookReviewTitle">Digital Copyright: Protecting Intellectual Property on the Internet</span>
        <div class="ItemDetail">By
          <span id="Authors">Jessica Litman</span></div>
        <div class="ItemDetail">
